msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Basis</strong></span>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Do you want to go further?</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Wil je nog verder gaan?</strong></span>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>1. Canned responses</strong><br/><br/>Click \"<strong>Send message</"
"strong>\", then type <strong>\"::\"</strong> in the message content to "
"display canned responses in the system. Then just select the one you want, "
"click send, and the customer receives the message! It's that easy! <br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>1. Standaardantwoorden</strong><br/><br/>Klik op \"<strong>Bericht "
"verzenden</strong>\", typ vervolgens <strong>\"::\"</strong> in de "
"berichtinhoud om standaardantwoorden in het systeem weer te geven. Selecteer "
"vervolgens het gewenste antwoord, klik op verzenden en de klant ontvangt het "
"bericht! Zo eenvoudig is het! <br/><br/>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>2. Email templates</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>2. E-mailsjablonen</strong>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: "
"normal\"><b>CRM App</b>: Nurture long-term relationships by tracking client "
"interactions, preferences, and\n"
"                follow-up reminders in one central hub.</span></font><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"/></strong><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: "
"normal\"><b>CRM-app</b>: Onderhoud duurzame relaties door interacties met "
"klanten, voorkeuren en opvolgherinneringen in één centrale omgeving te "
"verzamelen.</span></font><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"/></strong><br/>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: "
"normal\"><b>Knowledge App</b>: Securely store and organize detailed patient "
"notes, treatment plans, and holistic\n"
"                health records for easy reference.</span></font></strong><br/"
">"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: "
"normal\"><b>Kennis-app</b>: Bewaar en structureer gedetailleerde "
"aantekeningen, behandelplannen en holistische gezondheidsgegevens op een "
"veilige manier, zodat je de informatie altijd snel terug kunt vinden.</"
"span></font></strong><br/>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Odoo for Therapy Practices</span></"
"strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Odoo voor Therapiepraktijken</span></"
"strong>"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email templates </strong>can be set up in the Email Templates "
"technical menu. To access it, admins can enable debug mode and search for "
"the \"Email Templates\" menu from the homescreen."
msgstr ""
"<strong>E-mailsjablonen</strong> kunnen worden ingesteld in het technische "
"menu 'E-mailsjablonen'. Om hier toegang toe te krijgen, kunnen beheerders de "
"debugmodus inschakelen en zoeken naar het menu \"E-mailsjablonen\" op het "
"startscherm."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> "
"Website </font></strong>in a few clicks. Get new leads or direct appointment "
"online in a few clicks."
msgstr ""
"Een gratis, gepersonaliseerde, geïntegreerde<strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\"> Website </font></strong>in een paar klikken. Ontvang nieuwe leads "
"of online geboekte afspraken in een paar klikken."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add an upfront payment in your Appointment Type."
msgstr "Voeg een vooruitbetaling toe in je Afspraaktype."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the Subscription App and invoice automatically based on a subscription "
"type."
msgstr ""
"Voeg de Abonnementen-app toe en factureer automatisch op basis van een "
"abonnementstype."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"After each appointment, you can use the <strong>same methods </strong>to "
"plan your next session with your patient."
msgstr ""
"Na elke afspraak kun je <strong>dezelfde methoden</strong> gebruiken om je "
"volgende sessie met je cliënt te plannen."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can also use the \"Log Note\" button on your contacts or "
"create a specific knowledge article (like this one) for each of your "
"patients."
msgstr ""
"Als alternatief kun je ook de knop 'Notitie loggen' in je contacten "
"gebruiken of voor elk van je cliënten een specifiek kennisartikel (zoals dit "
"artikel) aanmaken."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any meeting within Odoo contains a \"Notes\" field. Type, upload images, "
"create tables, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Elke afspraak in Odoo bevat een veld 'Notities'. Typ, upload afbeeldingen, "
"maak tabellen en nog veel meer."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As you qualify Emily's needs, you update the lead status to \"Qualified\" in "
"the CRM pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Als je de behoeften van Emily hebt geëvalueerd, werk je de leadstatus bij "
"naar \"Gekwalificeerd\" in de CRM-pijplijn."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Auto-post your invoice on a regular basis."
msgstr "Verzend je facturen automatisch op regelmatige tijdstippen."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Automated recurring invoicing with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Subscription App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Automatische terugkerende facturatie met de <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Abonnementen-app</font></strong>."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model:mail.template,name:wellness_practitioner.booking_suggestion
msgid "Book your next appointment"
msgstr "Boek je volgende afspraak"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By installing this package, you'll have access to a range of essential apps, "
"including CRM, Appointment and Invoicing. Let's explore how these modules "
"can streamline your therapy practice operations."
msgstr ""
"Door dit pakket te installeren krijg je toegang tot een aantal essentiële "
"apps, waaronder CRM, Afspraken en Facturatie. Laten we eens kijken hoe deze "
"modules de activiteiten van je therapiepraktijk kunnen stroomlijnen."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few contacts."
msgstr ""
"Door de demodata van deze module te uploaden, is je database gevuld met een "
"aantal contacten."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click \"<strong>Send message</strong>\", then click the \"<strong>Expand</"
"strong>\" button on the bottom right of the composer."
msgstr ""
"Klik op '<strong>Bericht verzenden</strong>' en klik vervolgens op de knop "
"'<strong>Volledige editor openen</strong>' rechtsonder in de editor."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Ontdek meer over Odoo door in onze"

